id":"41cc2ee96827b1f031516ac3d2bcd155361fa268","tid":1909620,"uid":351046,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:35:51.000Z","msg":"條仔心諗今次玩大左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:16:09.000Z","msg":"等換器官基本上同聽天由命一撚樣，唔換死硬，換咗都唔代表過關，邊有得玩唔玩大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df9748edd26045ab9136791c131a6f02eba7a25b","tid":1909620,"uid":122331,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:17:37.000Z","msg":"起碼換咗個用到嘅肺<br />\n而且個女仔無吸煙習慣 用到已經好好"}]}